      "bookmarkId": "38382077_29_5910-6028",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "5910-6028",
      "markText": "‘天下战国，五胜者祸，四胜者弊[2]，三胜者霸，二胜者王，一胜者帝。’是以数胜得天下者稀[3]，以亡者众。”",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38382077&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=5910&rangeEnd=6028",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee132ec07249a9fdee179e3?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=5910&rangeEnd=6028"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38382077_7_5428-5453",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5428-5453",
      "markText": "因为抱必死决心的人和尽量求生的人，本来就是不等同的",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38382077&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5428&rangeEnd=5453",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee132ec07249a9fdee179e3?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5428&rangeEnd=5453"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38382077_6_3308-3468",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3308-3468",
      "markText": "将者，上不制[5]于天，下不制于地，中不制于人。宽不可激而怒，清不可事[6]以财。夫心狂、目盲、耳聋，以三悖[7]率人者，难矣。",
      "totalCount": 44,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38382077&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3308&rangeEnd=3468",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee132ec07249a9fdee179e3?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3308&rangeEnd=3468"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38382077_29_5490-5544",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "5490-5544",
      "markText": "夏民都很高兴，周武王讨伐殷纣王的时候，殷人却不反对。这是由于他们发起的战争顺应天理，合乎人情，所以才能这样啊",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38382077&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=5490&rangeEnd=5544",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee132ec07249a9fdee179e3?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=5490&rangeEnd=5544"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38382077_32_6001-6078",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "6001-6078",
      "markText": "一般来说，作战最重要的是，必须先去窥察敌将是谁，还要充分知晓他的才能，因为只有根据敌方军中的具体情况采取权变的方法，才能不费多大力气，就可以一举取得成功。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38382077&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=6001&rangeEnd=6078",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee132ec07249a9fdee179e3?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=6001&rangeEnd=6078"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38382077_5_1387-1449",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1387-1449",
      "markText": "黄帝曰：‘先神先鬼，先稽[9]我智。’谓之天官，人事而已。”",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38382077&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1387&rangeEnd=1449",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee132ec07249a9fdee179e3?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1387&rangeEnd=1449"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38382077_6_5004-5069",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5004-5069",
      "markText": "兵如植木，弩如羊角[7]，人人无不腾陵张胆，绝乎疑虑，堂堂决而去。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38382077&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5004&rangeEnd=5069",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee132ec07249a9fdee179e3?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5004&rangeEnd=5069"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38382077_31_5906-5938",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "5906-5938",
      "markText": "用兵的害处，当属犹豫最大，而全军失利的灾祸，多是产生于迟疑不决。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38382077&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=5906&rangeEnd=5938",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee132ec07249a9fdee179e3?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=5906&rangeEnd=5938"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38382077_35_4879-4921",
      "chapterUid": 35,
      "range": "4879-4921",
      "markText": "两军交战时，要先等敌军布好阵势之后，我们再击鼓进军，这样做的目的是为了表示我们的诚信",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38382077&chapterUid=35&rangeStart=4879&rangeEnd=4921",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee132ec07249a9fdee179e3?chapterUid=35&rangeStart=4879&rangeEnd=4921"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38382077_42_5384-5417",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "5384-5417",
      "markText": "在敌军尚未中计而还没有分散兵力之时，我们就要按兵不动，耐心等待战机",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38382077&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=5384&rangeEnd=5417",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee132ec07249a9fdee179e3?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=5384&rangeEnd=5417"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38382077_27_4097-4148",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "4097-4148",
      "markText": "善于抵御敌军的将领，都会先用大军和敌军正面交锋作战，然后出奇兵扼制敌军的要害，这就是交战必胜的战术了。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38382077&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=4097&rangeEnd=4148",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee132ec07249a9fdee179e3?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=4097&rangeEnd=4148"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38382077_29_7659-7733",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "7659-7733",
      "markText": "他们，对付强兵必须用谦让的姿态悦服他们，对付刚兵必须用强而有力的言辞说服他们，对付暴兵必须用诡诈的计谋制服他们，对付逆兵必须用权柄的威力压服他们。”",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38382077&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=7659&rangeEnd=7733",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee132ec07249a9fdee179e3?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=7659&rangeEnd=7733"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38382077_29_8951-9008",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "8951-9008",
      "markText": "古时候贤明的君王，一定会严谨地恪守君臣之间的礼节，整治尊卑上下之间的仪度，安抚并集中管理官吏与平民，使他们各得其所",
      "totalCount": 26,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38382077&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=8951&rangeEnd=9008",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee132ec07249a9fdee179e3?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=8951&rangeEnd=9008"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38382077_30_8329-8363",
